"title": "6222: rebellion, against God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6222",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The human race is in rebellion against God through its disobedience and unbelief.</p>\n<h2>Examples of rebellion against God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:2\">PSA 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:24\">NUM 20:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:14\">NUM 27:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:22-1Sam15:23\">1SA 15:22–15:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:7\">PSA 66:7</a></p>\n<h2>Warnings not to rebel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:14-1Sam12:15\">1SA 12:14–12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:9\">NUM 14:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num17:10\">NUM 17:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:10-Ps2:12\">PSA 2:10–2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek2:8\">EZK 2:8</a></p>\n<h2>Indignation expressed over rebellion against God</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:10\">PSA 5:10</a></p>\n<h2>The fate of the rebellious</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:24\">ISA 66:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:5\">DEU 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:6\">PSA 68:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer28:16\">JER 28:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:32\">JER 29:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:18\">LAM 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:20\">LAM 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:42\">LAM 3:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:16\">HOS 13:16</a></p>\n<h2>God is ready to forgive those who rebel against him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:8\">JER 33:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:5-Dan9:9\">DAN 9:5–9:9</a></p>\n<h2>The end times will be characterised by open rebellion against God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3\">2TH 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:18\">1JN 2:18</a></p>",
